msgctxt "72_Middle-aged Man"
msgid "Hiyori..."
msgstr "Hiyori..."

msgctxt "84_Middle-aged Man"
msgid "Why are you hanging out in a place like this!? You're going home right this instant, young lady!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96_Hiyori"
msgid "I'm not a child anymore! I don't have to listen to you, or anyone!"
msgstr "¡Ya no soy una niña! ¡Ya no tengo que escucharte a ti, ni a nadie!"

msgctxt "108_Hiyori"
msgid "I can't believe you went through my cell phone to snoop on me! That is seriously messed up!"
msgstr "¡No puedo creer que revisaras mi telefono para espiarme! ¡Eso está muy mal!"

msgctxt "120_Middle-aged Man"
msgid "I just wanted to make sure you're not mixed up with a bad crowd, that's all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132_Hiyori"
msgid "And what gives you the right to decide if my friends are \"good\" or \"bad,\" huh!?"
msgstr "¿Y qué te da el derecho a decidir si mis amigos son \"buenos\" o \"malos\", ¡eh!?"

msgctxt "144_Middle-aged Man"
msgid "I'm your father! That gives me the right! It's my job to look after you, to protect you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156_Hiyori"
msgid "Well, I don't need you to protect me anymore! I'm leaving and never coming back!"
msgstr "¡Bueno, ya no necesito que me protejas! ¡Me voy y no volvere nunca más!"

msgctxt "180_Middle-aged Man"
msgid "Hey! Wait!"
msgstr "¡Oye, espera!"

